data.description: Amazing 4 Bedroom 3-Bath Home in Northwest Local School District. The Home features an open concept kitchen, a walk out deck with attached gas fire pit and grill. The deck is built to accommodate an above ground pool. A fenced in back yard, All in a Quiet and friendly neighborhood. All kitchen Appliances Stay. Hot Tub Stays. Seller is offering a $5,000.00 credit toward a new pool. Schedule your Tour Today!
